              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 820,
              "content": "Soleur vs. Cursor and GitHub Copilot",
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
              "fontSize": 40,
              "fontWeight": "500"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "3J9HS",
              "name": "cmpP1",
              "fill": "#848484",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 780,
              "content": "Cursor and Copilot help you write code. Soleur helps you run a company — agents for marketing, legal, finance, sales, and more, not just engineering.",
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "V5ffz",
              "name": "cmpP2",
              "fill": "#848484",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 780,
              "content": "The core difference is memory. Soleur maintains a persistent, compounding knowledge base across every department. Cursor and Copilot start fresh every session. Soleur remembers.",
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
